Package: psychds
Title: Tools for Creating and Validating Psych-DS Datasets
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Brian", "Leonard", email = "bleonard@mit.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a Shiny application and helper functions for creating,
    validating, and managing datasets that conform to the Psych-DS standard
    (<https://psych-ds.github.io/>). Includes tools for building data
    dictionaries, generating dataset metadata, validating directory structure
    and filenames, and uploading datasets to the Open Science Framework (OSF).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/psych-ds/psychds-r
BugReports: https://github.com/psych-ds/psychds-r/issues
